text: Chalermsakdi Inswang (born 7 November 1926) is a Thai former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics and 1962 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Thai male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Thailand Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nakhon Sawan Province Category:Shooters at the 1962 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Thailand
